name: Sneakers
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

Sneakers

"Ayo fam, you here for some new drip?

Don't worry, I gotchu. We just got ahold of some fancy new sneakers. Man you're gonna love 'em."

Yep, it's right this way.

This way to get your sneakers!

IMPORTANT INFORMATION:

Because of the poses in my dataset, it's possible to encounter many weird poses. DO NOT FORGET that controlnet can fix poses! Get creative with this LoRA and remember that every tool has its limitations!

ADDITIONNALLY, I recommend NeverEndingDream with this model, very few errors.
